      "body" : "@Volksman sure, and sometimes you are stuck with stupid decisions others have made. Using a little bit of code to fix this isn&#39;t harmful. If you&#39;re in the position to, it puts you on the path to using better approaches. I wouldn&#39;t write a component ui framework inside of a JSP, granted, but I think it is perhaps this stupid opinion that you should &#39;never&#39; use code in a jsp that led to it taking so long for e.g. the component orientated approach to latch on."
