    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>In case you use JSTL and you wish to import a class in a tag page instead of a jsp page, the syntax is a little bit different. Replace the word 'page' with the word 'tag'.</p>\n\n<p>Instead of Sandman's correct answer</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;%@page import=\"path.to.your.class\"%&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>use</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;%@tag import=\"path.to.your.class\"%&gt;\n</code></pre>\n"
  } ],
